OL,3,CCarer's Allowance overpayment debt up
OL,4,Cby #100 million since 2018
OL,6,FOutstanding Carer's Allowance
OL,7,Foverpayment debt has risen to more
OL,8,Fthan #250 million, up by #100 million
OL,9,Fon six years ago, according to a new
OL,10,Freport.
OL,12,FThe public spending watchdog said the
OL,13,Fnumber of people with outstanding
OL,14,Foverpayment debt has risen every year
OL,15,Fsince 2018, and is up by almost three
OL,16,Fquarters from 80,169 people to 136,730
OL,17,Fin 2023/24.
