OL,3,CCarer's Allowance overpayment debt up
OL,4,Cby #100 million since 2018
OL,6,FThe issue of carer's allowance
OL,7,Foverpayment is already the subject of
OL,8,Fa Government-ordered review, due to
OL,9,Freport to ministers by summer next
OL,10,Fyear.
OL,12,FHistoric overpayments have led to many
OL,13,Fcarers ` who must earn #151 a week or
OL,14,Fless to qualify for the allowance `
OL,15,Funwittingly racking up unmanageable
OL,16,Flevels of debt and some quitting their
OL,17,Fjobs as a result.
