OL,3,CCarer's Allowance overpayment debt up
OL,4,Cby #100 million since 2018
OL,6,FThe issue of people being penalised
OL,7,Ffor going over their earnings limit
OL,8,Ffor carer's allowance even by as
OL,9,Flittle as a few pence per week has
OL,10,Fpreviously been branded a "scandal" by
OL,11,Fcharities.
OL,13,FThe earnings threshold will rise to
OL,14,F#196 a week from April.
OL,16,FThe National Audit Office (NAO), in a
OL,17,Freport published on Wednesday covering
OL,18,FEngland, Scotland and Wales, said the
OL,19,FDepartment for Work and Pensions (DWP)
OL,20,Fpaid #3.7 billion in Carer's Allowance
OL,21,Fto over 900,000 claimants in 2023/24.
