OL,6,FTotal outstanding overpayment debt in
OL,7,F2023-24 amounted to #251.7 million, up
OL,8,Ffrom #150.2 million in 2018-19 but
OL,9,Fdown slightly from #252.7 million in
OL,10,F2021/22, the NAO said.
OL,12,FThere were between 32,500 and 60,800
OL,13,Fnew Carer's Allowance overpayments
OL,14,Feach year between 2018/19 and 2023/24,
OL,15,Fwith claimants having earnings
OL,16,Fexceeding the threshold accounting for
OL,17,F57.6% of overpayment cases detected in
OL,18,Fthe past year.
