OL,6,FThe NAO said DWP can write off debt if
OL,7,Fit assesses there is no realistic
OL,8,Fpossibility of recovering it, and
OL,9,Fwhere a claimant has been dead for
OL,10,Fmore than two years.
OL,12,FReferrals for prosecution for
OL,13,Foverpayments fell over the past six
OL,14,Fyears, as did administrative
OL,15,Fpenalties, while civil penalties of
OL,16,F#50, where DWP judges someone to have
OL,17,Fbeen negligent in failing to provide
OL,18,Faccurate information, rose by half.
