OL,6,FThere were 54 overpayment cases which
OL,7,FDWP referred for prosecution in 2023/
OL,8,F24, down from 246 in 2018/19.
OL,10,FAdministrative penalties, as an
OL,11,Falternative to prosecution, numbered
OL,12,F75, down from 774 in 2018/19.
OL,14,FThere were 30,129 civil penalties, up
OL,15,Fby around 50% from 20,023 in 2018-19,
OL,16,Fthe NAO said.
