OL,6,FThe Government, having announced its
OL,7,Freview in October, has said it is
OL,8,Fcommitted to learning lessons and
OL,9,Fgetting to grips with the issues
OL,10,Faround overpayments.
OL,12,FThe review will look at overpayments,
OL,13,Fwhat changes can be made to reduce the
OL,14,Frisk of such overpayments in future
OL,15,Fand what the department can do to
OL,16,Fsupport carers who have already
OL,17,Faccrued debts.
