OL,6,FHelen Walker, chief executive of
OL,7,FCarers UK said the report is "yet
OL,8,Ffurther evidence of a broken system
OL,9,Fthat is failing unpaid carers", and
OL,10,Fdescribed the rise in the number of
OL,11,Fpeople with outstanding debts as "a
OL,12,Fserious failure which has left
OL,13,Fthousands of carers experiencing
OL,14,Femotional distress and financial
OL,15,Fhardship for years".
